{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ab7207ec2b","title":"毛泽东等掉念阮志清进世的暗电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"952045feb2","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":8,"articleId":"ab7207ec2b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"9099be1da0","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"院志清，原任越南劳动党中央政治局委员、中央书记处书记、越南民主共和国国防委员会委员，1967年7月6日因病进世，享年53岁。"},{"id":"6376a6ad65","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"胡志明，当时任越南劳动党中央委员会主席、越南民主共和国主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"864940ef8e","type":"title","text":"毛泽东等慎念院志清逝世的暗电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b"},{"id":"9099be1da0","type":"paragraph","text":"胡志明主席同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b"},{"id":"6376a6ad65","type":"paragraph","text":"惊悉院志清同志突然因病逝世，至为衰痛。院志清同志是您的、也是我们的好同志、好战友，也是世界革命人民和被压追民族的好战友。他为越南的革命事业，为中越两国、两觉、两军的团结战斗友谊，作出了卓越的贡献。他的进世，是我们共同的革命事业的巨大损失。但是，他的光辉的榜样和影响是永远不会消进的，是会继续发扬光大的。务望节衰，保重您的身体健康。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b"},{"id":"1af5634625","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东林彪周恩来","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b"},{"id":"0a7fc8ba2f","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六七年七月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b"}],"page":{"id":"b5ffbe86cb","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ab7207ec2b","start":537,"end":537}}}},"__N_SSG":true}